ater Middle Ages it was overtaken by   John  , but continued to run second to that name until the 20th century, when the picture became more fragmented."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"William Elye was born in 1517, in Tenterden, Kent, England, United Kingdom as the son of Richard Smythe de Elye and Lady Sophie Townsend. He married Mary Ely about 1539, in Tenterden, Kent, England, United Kingdom. They were the parents of at least 1 son."},"et":{"1517–":"1517–Surnud","1505–Female":"1505–Surnud","1507–1550":"1507–1550","1514–1608":"1514–1608","1517–1546":"1517–1546","1517–Male":"1517–Surnud","1519–Male":"1519–Surnud","1532–1608":"1532–1608","1517–Female":"1517–Surnud","1545–1615":"1545–1615","1490–1538":"1490–1538","–1539":"–1539","1550":"1550","Abt 1539":"umbes 1539","1490":"1490","about 1506 ":"umbes 1506","1514":"1514","1546":"1546","1545":"1545","1532":"1532","1608":"1608","1519":"1519","1507":"1507","1517":"1517","1539":"1539","1538":"1538","1615":"1615","1505":"1505","Tenterden, Kent, England":"Tenterden, Kent, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","of Tenterden, Kent, England":"Tenterden, Kent, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Brampton, Cumberland, England, United Kingdom":"Brampton, Cumberland, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1517–":"1517–Kuollut","1505–Female":"1505–Kuollut","1507–1550":"1507–1550","1514–1608":"1514–1608","1517–1546":"1517–1546","1517–Male":"1517–Kuollut","1519–Male":"1519–Kuollut","1532–1608":"1532–1608","1517–Female":"1517–Kuollut","1545–1615":"1545–1615","1490–1538":"1490–1538","–1539":"–1539","1550":"1550","Abt 1539":"noin 1539","1490":"1490","about 1506 ":"noin 1506","1514":"1514","1546":"1546","1545":"1545","1532":"1532","1608":"1608","1519":"1519","1507":"1507","1517":"1517","1539":"1539","1538":"1538","1615":"1615","1505":"1505","Tenterden, Kent, England":"Tenterden, Kent, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","of Tenterden, Kent, England":"Tenterden, Kent, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Brampton, Cumberland, England, United Kingdom":"Brampto